### Bug fixes

* Resolve an issue when specifying `--conda-exe` with `micromamba` or `mamba`, mamba-based standalone binaries are now renamed to `micromamba` and a symbolic link to `_conda` is added for backwards compatibility. (#1033 via #1090)

